39void
40nv04_fifo_dma_object_dtor(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base, int cookie)
41{
42 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
43 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.device->imem;
44
45 mutex_lock(&chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.mutex);
46 nvkm_ramht_remove(imem->ramht, cookie);
47 mutex_unlock(&chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.mutex);
48}
49
50static int
51nv04_fifo_dma_object_ctor(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base,
52 struct nvkm_object *object)
53{
54 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
55 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.device->imem;
56 u32 context = 0x80000000 | chan->base.chid << 24;
57 u32 handle = object->handle;
58 int hash;
59
60 switch (object->engine->subdev.index) {
61 case NVKM_ENGINE_DMAOBJ:
62 case NVKM_ENGINE_SW : context |= 0x00000000; break;
63 case NVKM_ENGINE_GR : context |= 0x00010000; break;
64 case NVKM_ENGINE_MPEG : context |= 0x00020000; break;
65 default:
66 WARN_ON(1);
67 return -EINVAL;
68 }
69
70 mutex_lock(&chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.mutex);
71 hash = nvkm_ramht_insert(imem->ramht, object, chan->base.chid, 4,
72 handle, context);
73 mutex_unlock(&chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.mutex);
74 return hash;
75}
76
77void
78nv04_fifo_dma_fini(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base)
79{
80 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
81 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = chan->fifo;
82 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device;
83 struct nvkm_memory *fctx = device->imem->ramfc;
84 const struct nv04_fifo_ramfc *c;
85 unsigned long flags;
86 u32 mask = fifo->base.nr - 1;
87 u32 data = chan->ramfc;
88 u32 chid;
89
90 /* prevent fifo context switches */
91 spin_lock_irqsave(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
92 nvkm_wr32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHES, 0);
93
94 /* if this channel is active, replace it with a null context */
95 chid = nvkm_rd32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHE1_PUSH1) & mask;
96 if (chid == chan->base.chid) {
97 nvkm_mask(device, NV04_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_PUSH, 0x00000001, 0);
98 nvkm_wr32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHE1_PUSH0, 0);
99 nvkm_mask(device, NV04_PFIFO_CACHE1_PULL0, 0x00000001, 0);
100
101 c = fifo->ramfc;
102 do {
103 u32 rm = ((1ULL << c->bits) - 1) << c->regs;
104 u32 cm = ((1ULL << c->bits) - 1) << c->ctxs;
105 u32 rv = (nvkm_rd32(device, c->regp) & rm) >> c->regs;
106 u32 cv = (nvkm_ro32(fctx, c->ctxp + data) & ~cm);
107 nvkm_wo32(fctx, c->ctxp + data, cv | (rv << c->ctxs));
108 } while ((++c)->bits);
109
110 c = fifo->ramfc;
111 do {
112 nvkm_wr32(device, c->regp, 0x00000000);
113 } while ((++c)->bits);
114
115 nvkm_wr32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHE1_GET, 0);
116 nvkm_wr32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHE1_PUT, 0);
117 nvkm_wr32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHE1_PUSH1, mask);
118 nvkm_wr32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHE1_PUSH0, 1);
119 nvkm_wr32(device, NV04_PFIFO_CACHE1_PULL0, 1);
120 }
121
122 /* restore normal operation, after disabling dma mode */
123 nvkm_mask(device, NV04_PFIFO_MODE, 1 << chan->base.chid, 0);
124 nvkm_wr32(device, NV03_PFIFO_CACHES, 1);
125 spin_unlock_irqrestore(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
126}
127
128void
129nv04_fifo_dma_init(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base)
130{
131 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
132 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = chan->fifo;
133 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device;
134 u32 mask = 1 << chan->base.chid;
135 unsigned long flags;
136 spin_lock_irqsave(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
137 nvkm_mask(device, NV04_PFIFO_MODE, mask, mask);
138 spin_unlock_irqrestore(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
139}
140
141void *
142nv04_fifo_dma_dtor(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base)
143{
144 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
145 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = chan->fifo;
146 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device->imem;
147 const struct nv04_fifo_ramfc *c = fifo->ramfc;
148
149 nvkm_kmap(imem->ramfc);
150 do {
151 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + c->ctxp, 0x00000000);
152 } while ((++c)->bits);
153 nvkm_done(imem->ramfc);
154 return chan;
155}
156
157const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_func
158nv04_fifo_dma_func = {
159 .dtor = nv04_fifo_dma_dtor,
160 .init = nv04_fifo_dma_init,
161 .fini = nv04_fifo_dma_fini,
162 .object_ctor = nv04_fifo_dma_object_ctor,
163 .object_dtor = nv04_fifo_dma_object_dtor,
164};
165
166static int
167nv04_fifo_dma_new(struct nvkm_fifo *base, const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass,
168 void *data, u32 size, struct nvkm_object **pobject)
169{
170 struct nvkm_object *parent = oclass->parent;
171 union {
172 struct nv03_channel_dma_v0 v0;
173 } *args = data;
174 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = nv04_fifo(base);
175 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = NULL;
176 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device;
177 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = device->imem;
178 int ret;
179
180 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel dma size %d\n", size);
181 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
182 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel dma vers %d pushbuf %"PRIx64" "
183 "offset %08x\n", args->v0.version,
184 args->v0.pushbuf, args->v0.offset);
185 if (!args->v0.pushbuf)
186 return -EINVAL;
187 } else
188 return ret;
189
190 if (!(chan = kzalloc(sizeof(*chan), GFP_KERNEL)))
191 return -ENOMEM;
192 *pobject = &chan->base.object;
193
194 ret = nvkm_fifo_chan_ctor(&nv04_fifo_dma_func, &fifo->base,
195 0x1000, 0x1000, false, 0, args->v0.pushbuf,
196 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_DMAOBJ) |
197 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_GR) |
198 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_SW),
199 0, 0x800000, 0x10000, oclass, &chan->base);
200 chan->fifo = fifo;
201 if (ret)
202 return ret;
203
204 args->v0.chid = chan->base.chid;
205 chan->ramfc = chan->base.chid * 32;
206
207 nvkm_kmap(imem->ramfc);
208 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x00, args->v0.offset);
209 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x04, args->v0.offset);
210 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x08, chan->base.push->addr >> 4);
211 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x10,
212 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_TRIG_128_BYTES |
213 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_SIZE_128_BYTES |
214#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
215 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_BIG_ENDIAN |
216#endif
217 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_MAX_REQS_8);
218 nvkm_done(imem->ramfc);
219 return 0;
220}
221
222const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_oclass
223nv04_fifo_dma_oclass = {
224 .base.oclass = NV03_CHANNEL_DMA,
225 .base.minver = 0,
226 .base.maxver = 0,
227 .ctor = nv04_fifo_dma_new,
228};
